  "release_notes": "Production trigger rules turned back on. AnimationTrigger.TEST_MODE flipped from True (every Ready fires an animation — was set while iterating on choreography) to False (the real rate-limit kicks in). An animation now requires: at least 10 minutes elapsed since the previous qualifying Ready AND a qualifying-send count between 4 and 8 inclusive (the target is re-rolled randomly after each fire). Rapid clicks within the 10-minute window collapse into a single qualifying send so the bonus can't be farmed by spamming. State is in-memory only — restarting the app resets the counter.",
